Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}該相信什麼? 該選擇什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.65,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}即使沒有絕對的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}但只要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:52.71,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}就不會再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:36.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}まっさらな世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:41.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}何を君は描く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:59.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}混迷の展開は必然に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}容赦なく巻き込んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:07.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}透明な限界は裏腹に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}光と影が交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:16.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}目の前にある現実が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:23.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}続いてくと信じたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}走り出した歯車が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}冒険再び呼び醒ます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}欠けた記憶 手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}確かめてみたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}何を信じ? 選ぶのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}絶対の答えがなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}ただ君と 一緒なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:52.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}怖くはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:16.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}暗がりの中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}君は起き出し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}身支度をする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:36.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}もう 夜明けが近い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}山の形が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:50.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}ほんのり浮かぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:56.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}東の空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:04.03,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}ああ 鳥たちの群れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:11.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}悲しいこともあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:17.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}挫けることもあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:27.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}やれるだけやり切ったら後は食べて寝て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:34.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}さあ 続けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:16.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天色尚暗之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}你扶身而起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}整理好行裝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:36.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}轉眼 黎明已近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}山脈的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:50.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}隱約浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:56.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}東方天空上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:04.03,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}啊啊 一群鳥兒飛過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:11.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}一定經歷過悲傷吧
